      },
      "text": [
        "هُ دَخَلَ عَلَيْهِ نِسْوَةٌ فَسَأَلَتْهُ امْرَأَةٌ مِنْهُنَّ عَنِ السَّحْقِ فَقَالَ حَدُّهَا حَدُّ الزَّانِي فَقَالَتِ الْمَرْأَةُ مَا ذَكَرَ اللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ ذَلِكَ فِي الْقُرْآنِ فَقَالَ بَلَى قَالَتْ وَ أَيْنَ هُوَ قَالَ هُنَّ أَصْحَابُ الرَّسِّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Muhammad Bin Abu Hamza and Hisham and hafs, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, some women having come over to him, so a woman from them asked him<sup>asws</sup> about the lesbianism. So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) is the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) of the adulterer’. So the woman said, ‘Allah<sup>azwj</sup> Mighty and Majestic has not Mentioned that in the Quran?’ So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Yes’. She said, ‘And where is it?’ He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘These are <span class=\"ibTxt\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:25#h38\"><a href=\"/books/quran:25#h38\">[25:38]</a></a> the dwellers of the Al-Rass</span>’."
        ]
      }
    }
